title: The Football League Show 09.08.2014
description:
The Football League Show
Saturday 9th August 2014 

Highlights and analysis from the Football League, presented by Manish Bhasin. As the new season kicks off, he has the best of the action from Portman Road as Fulham start life back in the Championship at Ipswich. Cardiff are at Blackburn and there are highlights from a London derby as newly-promoted Brentford welcome Charlton to Griffin Park.
